    "For different chapters of the Book of Changes, we gauged their popularity based on the number of reused sentences.",
    "It can be observed that in all three screenshots, the largest rectangular sections correspond to the summary chapters of the Book of Changes, Xi Ci (系辞), which stands out with the most frequently reused sentences among all three collections, confirming its expected prominence.",
    "We also noticed that the chapter-level distribution of reused frequency varies across the three literature collections.",
    "There are clear differences in intertextuality distribution within and outside disciplines: In Fig. 11a, the distribution of sizes among rectangles of different colors is relatively uniform.",
    "However, in Fig. 11b, c, there is a greater disparity in the sizes of rectangles."
